      Mesa Royalty Trust News           






Mesa Royalty Trust Announces Trust Income for July 2017
7/19/17 5:01 pm CDTHOUSTON--(BUSINESS WIRE)--Mesa Royalty Trust (NYSE: MTR) announced the Trust income distribution 
      for the month of July 2017. Unitholders of record on July 31, 2017 will 
      receive distributions amounting to $0.116040980 per unit payable on 
      October 31, 2017. The Trust received $97,762 and $47,841 from the New 
      Mexico and Colorado portions of the San Juan Basin Properties. Royalty 
      income from the Hugoton Properties totaled $85,826.
    
    
      This press release contains forward-more...


Mesa Royalty Trust Announces Trust Income for June 2017
6/16/17 4:47 pm CDTHOUSTON--(BUSINESS WIRE)--Mesa Royalty Trust (NYSE: MTR) announced the Trust income distribution 
      for the month of June 2017. Unitholders of record on June 30, 2017 will 
      receive distributions amounting to $0.098156071 per unit payable on 
      July 31, 2017. The Trust received $64,932 and $41,910 from the New 
      Mexico and Colorado portions of the San Juan Basin Properties. Royalty 
      income from the Hugoton Properties totaled $86,749.
    
    
      This press release contains forward-more...


Mesa Royalty Trust Announces Trust Income for May 2017
5/18/17 4:55 pm CDTHOUSTON--(BUSINESS WIRE)--Mesa Royalty Trust (NYSE: MTR) announced the Trust income distribution 
      for the month of May 2017. Unitholders of record on May 31, 2017 will 
      receive distributions amounting to $0.112244121 per unit payable on 
      July 31, 2017. The Trust received $75,664 and $49,573 from the New 
      Mexico and Colorado portions of the San Juan Basin Properties. Royalty 
      income from the Hugoton Properties totaled $103,409.
    
    
      This press release contains forward-more...


 
 

